00:17:37.699 --> 00:17:41.699
Like we, it's a lot of the time, we're in the process of trying to figure out what's the best way to do it.

00:17:42.099 --> 00:17:45.000
a lot of times, honestly it's driven by groupings of models.

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:51.300
So it makes sense to have the model engines for sure event time data for the most part uncensored.

00:17:51.300 --> 00:17:54.599
